Road_traffic is a Node.js program that checks for the traffic situation in lagos roads by fetching traffic data from tsobion.com.

Introduction

1. check_traffic is a Node.js command line program that checks the current traffic on a road in lagos city.
2. it has the following features;
 . --list Displays all the traffic new being tracked.
 . --road [road] Displays the traffic status of a road.

 Dependencies

 . Node.Js - A JavaScript runtime to run javascript code outside a browser effectively.
 . request - A Node.Js module to fetch data from a web API
 . npm  - Node Package Manager for open source libraries
 . jasmine - JavaScript unit testing framework.
 
 How to Use
 To run test
  . cd into the project root directory and
     run npm test
 To use the functionalities
 . cd into the project root director and run
   node check_traffic.js [-option]
